thake the pot and put is on the gas
turn on the gas to high hit to boil the water 
add a pinch of salt to the water
after the water is boiling add the fresh penne pasta
set the timer for 10 min
after 10 min take out the pasta with skimmer and put it in the pan
take the canned alfredo sauce from the fridge 
turn the hit to medium and add pasta and alfredo sauce to the pan
mix it well for 5 min
put the pasta in the pasta plate 
add some fresh chopped parsley on top of pasta
serve it on the table and put fork on the side
